<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Herakleopolite</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Εὐρυ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λόχ</unclear>ῳ συγγενεῖ καὶ στρατηγῶι καὶ 

    <lb n="2"/>ἐπὶ τῶν προσόδων 

    <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">πα</supplied>ρὰ Τασέμθεως γυναικὸς Ὥρου ἀδελφοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Ἑριέ</supplied>ως τοῦ πτεραφόρου ἱερέως τοῦ ἐν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Τιλώ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">θ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ει</unclear> 

    <lb n="5"/>ἱεροῦ Ἡρακλέους θεοῦ μεγίστου. τῶν γονέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ω</supplied>ν μου 

    <lb n="6"/>ἐκ Ποενάμεως εἰς τὸ ἐν τῆι Τιλώθει κατελ-

    <lb n="7"/>θόντων <add place="supralinear">ἱερὸν</add> καὶ εἰς τὸ τῶν προγεγραμμένων 

    <lb n="8"/>παστοφόριον καταλυσάντω<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> ἐπιπλεκείς μοι 

    <lb n="9"/>ὁ Ὧρος ἐκ πολλῆς διατριβῆς. ὁ πατὴρ ἀποθ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">έ</supplied>-

    <lb n="10"/>μενος τὰ ἐν τῆι ἰδίαι ὑπάρχοντα καὶ φερνὴν 

    <lb n="11"/>αὐτῶι διὰ τῶν ἀδελφῶν τοῦ τε Ἑριέως καὶ Σεμθέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ως</supplied> 

    <lb n="12"/>Παάβιος προσενεγκάμενος <expan>χα<ex cert="high">λκοῦ</ex></expan> <expan>νο<ex cert="high">μίσματος</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντα</ex></expan> <num value="25">κε</num>. ἔγραψέν 

    <lb n="13"/>μοι Αἰγυπτι´αν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τροφῖ</unclear>τιν, ἐξ οὗ καὶ ἐσχηκυῖα 

    <lb n="14"/>τέκνα <num value="4">δ</num>, ἀ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">πὸ δὲ το</supplied>ύτων ἑνὸς <num value="1"/> π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ερ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ιόντος</supplied>. 

    <lb n="15"/>οἱ ἀδελφοὶ ἀνή<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">νεγκ</unclear>αν αὐτῶι τῶν οἰκη<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μά</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τω</unclear>ν 

    <lb n="16"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied>ιαίρεσιν. ὁ ἀνὴρ μεταλλάξας τὸν βίον 

    <lb n="17"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὕτ</unclear>ως διακείμενος. ἐμὲ ἠνάγκασαν μέχρι τοῦ 

    <lb n="18"/>νῦν τὰς ἐν ταῖς νεκρίαις εἰς αὐτὸν δαπάνας 

    <lb n="19"/>ποιεῖσθαι, πάντα τὰ τοῦ τέκνου ἀποφερόμενοι 

    <lb n="20"/>οὐδὲν εἰς τὰ ἀναγκαῖα ἐπιχορηγοῦσι. διὸ <choice><corr>ἀξιῶ</corr><sic>αξιωι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="21"/>χήρα οὖσα ἐκθεῖναί μοι καὶ τῶι ὀρφανῶι 

    <lb n="22"/>παιδίωι τὸ δίκαιον μὴ ἐμμεμενηκότ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear> ἐφ᾽ οἷς 

    <lb n="23"/>οἱ ἱερεῖς καὶ Ἀπίων ὁ γυμνασιαρχήσας <choice><corr>δεδικαιώκασι</corr><sic>δεδικαιωκαν</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="24"/>ἐὰν φαίνηται προνοῆσαι ἡμῶν, ἵν᾽ ὦμεν βεβοηθημένοι. 

    <lb n="25"/><space extent="unknown" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/> <note lang="en" anchored="yes" place="not specified">m2 ?</note> εὐτύχει </ab></div><div n="meta.4928" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.4928" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low">ca. 47 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.4928" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. Mooren, Aulic Titulature, S. 113, Nr. 0106.</p></div><div n="meta.4928" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">BGU</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1849</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">4928</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0001</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1849</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0001;8;1849" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.4928" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.4928" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><geogName type="nome" cert="high" full="yes">Herakleopolites</geogName>, <geogName type="ancientRegion" key="Aegyptus" cert="high" full="yes">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>